Linezolid was initially approved in 2000 and was the first member of the oxazolidinone antibiotic class.[A233425] A second member of this class, [tedizolid], was approved by the FDA in 2014 and is considered generally more effective and tolerable than its predecessor.', '["J01XX08"]', '[]');
